76561197972409186,Recommended,256370,17408482,"Posted: 5 August, 2015",all,Sternn,"First, don't let the screen shots fool you into thinking they're only from a prerender cinematic. No, these are in game results that quickly grab your eyeballs and attempt to pull'em from your sockets!Unlike most motorcycle racers out there, this one definately requires you to pay close attention to not only your speed while cornering, but the use of rider leaning plus turning the bike. Yes, you better let off that throttle else it's into the hay stacks, crowds, and trees.Very, very different--and not made easy by default! Even with all driving assists enabled, and NPC racers AI set to basic, you will need some patience and determination to succeed at avoiding last place or DNF ranking in every race.With that all said, I love this game. Although only scratching the surface thus far, it looks, sounds and feels as expected in a true racing sim. And don't get me started on the personal satisfaction of riding over my buddy, laughing my head off and suddenly taking a dirt-dive myself. Now we both laugh!"
